{"tid":1264920,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【紐約即時】在美港人紐約中央車站集會 表達反對逃犯條例修訂","createTime":"2019-06-29T02:38:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T04:25:06.000Z","uid":147416,"like":47,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1b2824aa349f5efaa205596f64b0ec1fc37f966b","tid":1264920,"uid":147416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T02:38:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/279926822076021/posts/2316474861754530?s=1000124775&amp;sfns=xmwa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F279926822076021%2Fposts%2F2316474861754530%3Fs%3D1000124775%26sfns%3Dxmwa&d=Ns8Dgi7AEu9liZcLsKty6j4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=28d9be10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/279926822076021/posts/2316474861754530?s=1000124775&amp;sfns=xmwa</a><br />\n<br />\n【紐約即時】在美港人紐約中央車站集會 表達反對逃犯條例修訂<br />\n<br />\n現場有約百人穿著黑衣默站，並舉起紐約時報印有「STAND WITH HONG KONG AT G20」的廣告版面，以表達他們反對香港送中條例。民眾亦將報紙傳遞給途人，以將信息傳遞出去，過程中有外國途人參與默站。<br />\n<br />\n是次活動由 NY4HK 發起，於紐約時間28日晚上7時45分在紐約中央車站（Grand Central Terminal）開始，穿著黑衣高舉報紙5分鐘。大會建議參與者帶備兩份紐約時報，一份舉起，另一份邀請路人一起參與。"},{"pid":"793fa9b77475605acf918b10f95cc406f379a919","tid":1264920,"uid":257422,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T02:39:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/65551173_2316642361737780_3071769178558955520_o.jpg?_nc_cat=101&amp;efg=eyJpIjoidCJ9&amp;_nc_oc=AQmDso0xmReNduCs9p-bWZa7ZzsjoXh3uPsW95WEFbPO0DSgndeV6wBkEDIQsUzhpu4&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-2.fna&amp;oh=a2eb0af6a217c5fc2646c1f0d6189e76&amp;oe=5DC5EBA1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F65551173_2316642361737780_3071769178558955520_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D101%26efg%3DeyJpIjoidCJ9%26_nc_oc%3DAQmDso0xmReNduCs9p-bWZa7ZzsjoXh3uPsW95WEFbPO0DSgndeV6wBkEDIQsUzhpu4%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-2.fna%26oh%3Da2eb0af6a217c5fc2646c1f0d6189e76%26oe%3D5DC5EB